Dubai - Ras al-Khaimah
As a Order Taker, you are responsible for providing Guests with food and drinks as requested in an efficient manner and according to proper procedure and regulations. A Order Taker carries the responsibility of thoroughly understanding the menu, food offerings and food contents. Positive attitude and excellent communication skills.
Nice tone of voice. Up selling skills. Flexible schedule must be able to work Night and weekends. Good command of Written and Oral English, local language and other European languages would be advantageous Previous experience working as in a food and beverage environment
